# UDS Source Repo Marker
# This file signals to the UDS CLI that the current directory is the
# Universal Development Standards source repository itself, not an
# adopter project.
#
# Presence of this file causes `uds update`, `uds check`, and `uds init`
# to refuse running (see DEC-044 / XSPEC-071). Use `scripts/bump-version.sh`
# or `npm run docs:sync` for source-repo maintenance instead.
